entries.femaleVariant: You think it's better out east?
I don't know, but I'd sure like to find out. I've got family in Nebraska, we could stop there a while.
Heard a good gig's hard to find out there.
It's hard in Night City, too.
Sure, because I know what I'd find. I'd rather live a while longer, thanks.
Ehh, you just never looked in the right place. Or for the right gig.
Well, safe travels then. Maybe Nebraska'll be kinder to you.
